data.text:
Antiquariat Daša Pahor is on the brink of exciting changes, as we are moving to a fresh, modernized location.

You will note a brief pause in our online store from mid-August to the end of September.

This is a necessary step for us to fine-tune and enhance our services. Do not worry, our offers and catalogues are not going anywhere during this period.

Feel free to reach out to us anytime via telephone, WhatsApp, or email at antiquariat@pahor.de. We’re here to help!

Your patience and support make this move possible, and we cannot wait to serve you better from our new premises.

Have a good summer!

Yours,

Daša & Alex
